tourBios.carHigh: Has never played on the PGA TOUR or Nationwide Tour...Played on the Hooters Tour from 2007-2010.
tourBios.personal: Lists Rob Noel as his golf instructor...Favorite course played is The Club at Porto Cima...Never travels without Diet Mountain Dew...First car was a Hyundai Excel...Favorite movie is "Gladiator." Favorite food is Bop's Frozen Custard. Favorite city to visit is Pensacola, FL...Bucket list includes playing in the World Series of Poker...Not many people know that he gets pedicures...Charities involved in include Metairie (LA) Humane Society, with an emphasis on animal rescue, Safe Harbor Battered Women's Shelter and the American Red Cross.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the Web.com Tour was T15th in 2011 at the BMW Charity Pro-Am presented by SYNNEX Corporation.
